    type: 'knowledge',
    content: "# TikTok Lead Generation Strategy\n\n## The Opportunity\n\nTikTok is **the discovery engine** - viral potential unmatched.\n\n- **1+ billion monthly active users**\n- **Highest organic reach of any platform**\n- **Algorithm rewards content, not followers**\n- **25-45 demo growing fastest**\n- **Commerce features expanding**\n\n**One viral video can generate more leads than a month of other platforms.**\n\n---\n\n## Platform Mechanics\n\n### Algorithm Priorities (2026)\n\n1. **Watch time** - Completion rate is king\n2. **Replays** - Strong signal of value\n3. **Shares** - Viral amplification\n4. **Comments** - Engagement depth\n5. **Follows from video** - Conversion signal\n\n### Content Distribution\n\n| Factor | Impact |\n|--------|--------|\n| First 3 seconds | Make or break |\n| Video length | 30-60s sweet spot |\n| Trending audio | 2-3x reach boost |\n| Hashtags | Discovery, not reach |\n| Posting time | 6-9pm local best |\n\n---\n\n## Account Strategy\n\n### Main Account: @garthbid\n\n**Content pillars:**\n1. Equipment reveals (satisfying content)\n2. Auction drama (bidding wars)\n3. Price reveals (what things sold for)\n4. Transformation (before/after)\n5. Behind-the-scenes (auction chaos)\n\n### Niche Accounts\n\n| Account | Focus | Content Style |\n|---------|-------|---------------|\n| @dieseltok | Trucks & diesel | Truck content, sound, power |\n| @tractortok | Farm equipment | Satisfying farm content |\n| @equipmentfinds | Finds & deals | \"Found this for $X\" |\n| @auctionaddicts | Auction culture | Drama, competition |\n| @barnfinds | Hidden treasures | Reveal content |\n\n---\n\n## Content Strategy\n\n### Video Formats That Work\n\n**1. The Reveal (BEST PERFORMER)**\n```\nHook: \"What's under this tarp?\"\nSetup: Dusty barn, mystery object\nReveal: Slow pan to beautiful equipment\nPayoff: Price/value reveal\nCTA: \"Would you bid?\"\n```\n\n**2. The Price Game**\n```\nHook: \"Guess the price - closest wins\"\nContent: Show equipment from all angles\nReveal: Actual auction result\nCTA: \"Follow for more price reveals\"\n```\n\n**3. The Drama**\n```\nHook: \"Two bidders went to WAR over this\"\nContent: Screen recording of bid battle\nClimax: Final bid moment\nCTA: \"This could be you Monday\"\n```\n\n**4. The Transformation**\n```\nHook: \"He bought this for $5k...\"\nBefore: Rough equipment\nProcess: Quick clips of work\nAfter: Beautiful restoration\nReveal: \"Sold for $25k at auction\"\n```\n\n**5. The Satisfying**\n```\nHook: [No text, just satisfying visual]\nContent: Equipment starting up, moving, working\nAudio: Trending sound or raw engine\nCTA: \"Pure equipment therapy\"\n```\n\n**6. The Education**\n```\nHook: \"Why your tractor isn't selling\"\nContent: 3 quick tips\nEach tip: Visual demonstration\nCTA: \"Want the full guide? Link in bio\"\n```\n\n### Trending Audio Strategy\n\n**Categories to watch:**\n- Satisfying/ASMR sounds\n- Dramatic reveals\n- \"What I ordered vs what I got\"\n- Price/value reveals\n- Before/after trends\n\n**Execution:**\n- Check trending page daily\n- Adapt trends to equipment content\n- Jump on trends within 24-48 hours\n- Create original sounds from equipment\n\n---\n\n## Lead Generation Tactics\n\n### Tactic 1: Comment Section Mining\n\n**Monitor comments for:**\n- \"I need one of these\"\n- \"Where can I get one?\"\n- \"How much would this cost?\"\n- \"I have one to sell\"\n\n**Response:**\n```\nCheck the link in bio - we auction \nequipment like this every Monday üëÄ\n```\n\n### Tactic 2: Duet/Stitch Strategy\n\n**Find videos of:**\n- Equipment for sale posts\n- Pricing questions\n- \"What should I sell this for\"\n- Equipment complaints\n\n**Stitch with:**\n```\n\"When they don't know what their equipment is worth...\n\nThat's literally why auctions exist.\nLet buyers compete - price discovers itself.\n\nLink in bio if you want to learn more.\"\n```\n\n### Tactic 3: Live Auctions\n\n**Weekly TikTok Live:**\n- Broadcast Monday auction live\n- React to bids in real-time\n- Engage with comments\n- Build community\n\n**Benefits:**\n- High engagement\n- Real-time conversion\n- Community building\n- Platform boost for going live\n\n### Tactic 4: Creator Partnerships\n\n**Target creators:**\n- Farm/ranch TikTokers\n- Truck/diesel content\n- Tool restoration\n- Rural lifestyle\n\n**Offer:**\n- Feature their listings\n- Revenue share on conversions\n- Free promotion\n- Collaboration content\n\n---\n\n## Agent Deployment\n\n### Agent Type: Content Creator\n\n**Output:**\n- 3-5 videos per day\n- Trending audio monitoring\n- Comment engagement\n- Performance analysis\n\n**Tools:**\n- CapCut for editing\n- TikTok native for posting\n- Trending sound trackers\n- Analytics dashboards\n\n### Agent Type: Live Host\n\n**Responsibilities:**\n- Host Monday auction lives\n- Engage with audience\n- Answer questions real-time\n- Convert viewers to bidders\n\n### Agent Type: Community Manager\n\n**Responsibilities:**\n- Monitor all comments\n- Reply to inquiries\n- DM interested users\n- Track leads\n\n---\n\n## Growth Tactics\n\n### The Volume Play\n\n**Strategy:** Post more, learn faster\n\n**Execution:**\n- 3 videos minimum per day\n- Test different formats\n- Double down on winners\n- Kill underperformers\n\n**Why it works:** TikTok algorithm gives every video a chance. More videos = more lottery tickets.\n\n### The Series Strategy\n\n**Create recurring series:**\n- \"Monday Auction Results\"\n- \"What's This Worth Wednesday\"\n- \"Friday Finds\"\n- \"Barn Reveal Sunday\"\n\n**Benefits:**\n- Viewer anticipation\n- Return visits\n- Binge watching\n- Playlist organization\n\n### The Sound Strategy\n\n**Create original sounds:**\n- Auction countdown sounds\n- \"SOLD!\" sound effect\n- Equipment startup sounds\n- Bidding war sounds\n\n**Benefit:** Others use your sound = free promotion\n\n---\n\n## TikTok Shop Integration\n\n### Future Opportunity\n\n**TikTok Shop features:**\n- Product links in videos\n- Live shopping\n- Affiliate marketplace\n- Direct checkout\n\n**Garthbid application:**\n- Link to listings from videos\n- Live auction shopping events\n- Affiliate program for creators\n- \"Buy now\" for fixed-price items\n\n---\n\n## Metrics & KPIs\n\n| Metric | Target | Measurement |\n|--------|--------|-------------|\n| Videos posted | 100+/month | Volume |\n| Total views | 1M+/month | Reach |\n| Followers | 50k in 90 days | Audience |\n| Avg watch time | 80%+ | Quality |\n| Comments | 100+/video avg | Engagement |\n| Profile visits | 10k+/week | Interest |\n| Link clicks | 1k+/week | Intent |\n| Leads generated | 50+/week | Pipeline |\n\n---\n\n## 90-Day Roadmap\n\n### Days 1-30: Foundation\n- [ ] Create/optimize accounts\n- [ ] Establish content templates\n- [ ] Post 3x daily minimum\n- [ ] Study performing content\n- [ ] Build content library\n\n### Days 31-60: Scale\n- [ ] Launch niche accounts\n- [ ] Increase to 5x daily\n- [ ] Start TikTok Lives\n- [ ] Creator outreach\n- [ ] Series content live\n\n### Days 61-90: Dominate\n- [ ] 10+ accounts running\n- [ ] Weekly Lives established\n- [ ] Creator partnerships live\n- [ ] Viral content playbook\n- [ ] Predictable lead flow\n\n---\n\n## The Vision\n\nTikTok is **the wildcard that can change everything.**\n\nOne video can:\n- Generate 1M views overnight\n- Drive 10,000 profile visits\n- Create 1,000 leads\n- Result in 100 listings\n\nThe algorithm doesn't care how big you are. It cares if your content slaps.\n\n**Make content that slaps ‚Üí Get discovered ‚Üí Convert discovery to listings**\n\nüî®\n\n---\n\n*Last Updated: 2026-01-31*\n",
